# Input

```yml
# Tabs and spaces
quoted: "Quoted 	"
block:	|
  void main() {
  	printf("Hello, world!\n");
  }

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@
 # Tabs and spaces
